### 3. Register Agent with BDS License Metadata
```bash
curl -X POST "https://registry.masumi.network/api/agents" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer public-test-key-masumi-registry-c23f3d21" \
  -d '{
    "did": "did:cardano:freevoices-tibet-lotus-001",
    "name": "FreeVoicesTibetArchiver",
    "description": "ShalomXEdge bodhicitta ZK-oracle archiving Tibetan Mahayana teachings & FreeVoices testimonies. Special BDS Royalty License v1.0 ‚Äì 8% to ActInnovations / Informaci√≥n Incentiverse Inc, Texas",
    "license": "Special BDS (Bodhicitta Dharma Shalom) Royalty License v1.0 ‚Äì 8% commercial royalty to ActInnovations / Informaci√≥n Incentiverse Inc, Texas",
    "tags": ["tibet", "mahayana", "free-tibet", "bodhicitta", "shalomxedge", "bds-royalty", "actinnovations", "incentiverse"]
  }'
```
‚Üí Copy the returned `identifier` ‚Üí set as `AGENT_IDENTIFIER` in `.env`

